This paper is primarily focused on computer vision tasks such as semantic segmentation and object recognition, which suggests that it is likely to belong to the cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of multimodal approaches and self-supervised learning, which are relevant to robotics (cs.RO), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. However, since the paper's primary focus is on computer vision, cs.CV is the most likely sub-category.
